Unsourced material may be challenged and removed. *Find sources:* "Eunos Constituency" – news **·** newspapers **·** books **·** scholar **·** JSTOR *(January 2022)* *(Learn how and when to remove this message)* **Eunos Constituency** was a constituency in Singapore. It used to exist from 1984 to 1988, where it merged parts of Kaki Bukit and Tampines constituencies. It was absorbed into the namesake [Eunos Group Representation Constituency](/wiki/Eunos_Group_Representation_Constituency). ## Members of Parliament YearMember of ParliamentParty**1984**[Zulkifli Mohammed](/wiki/Zulkifli_Mohammed)[PAP](/wiki/People%27s_Action_Party) ## Electoral results Note: The [Elections Department](/wiki/Elections_Department_Singapore) does not include rejected votes when calculating the vote shares of candidates.
